select *
from (
select 
    'A' mil_status_code, 
    'Veteran' mil_status_desc
from dual
union
select 
    'B', 
    'Active Duty' 
from dual
union
select 
    'C', 
    'National Guard/Reserves' 
from dual
union
select 
    'D' , 
    'Spouse' 
from dual
union
select 
    'E' , 
    'Child' 
from dual
)
